text: Visualize a humorous scene featuring a green frog with swimming goggles. The frog exhibits almost human-like qualities as it sits in an office environment. It is sitting on a swivel chair, behind a large wooden desk piled with paperwork and a desktop computer. Paradoxically, the amphibian is fully prepared for a swim, yet finds itself in an entirely dry, corporate setup. The stern look on its face is accentuated by its crisp white shirt and black tie, making the situation even more amusing and unusual.
